stomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) explicitly extends to gaming and =
video streaming services as well, which could lead the Federal Trade Commis=
sion to scrutinize how streamers like Netflix, Amazon Prime, and YouTube al=
gorithmically curate content for viewers.

