          <td style=3D"padding-bottom: 36px; color: #000000; font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">When she won her Os=
car in 2018, <b>Frances McDormand</b> perfectly captured the zeitgeist with=
 an acceptance speech that concluded, =E2=80=9CI have two words to leave wi=
th you tonight, ladies and gentlemen: <i>inclusion rider</i>.=E2=80=9D Back=
 then, of course, Hollywood was the epicenter of resistance: to <b>Donald T=
rump</b>, to sexual harassment, to the lack of race and gender diversity in=
 entertainment. Hashtags like #MeToo and #OscarsSoWhite were buzzing on Twi=
tter, a platform <b>Elon Musk</b> had not yet colonized. McDormand=E2=80=99=
s proclamation seemed to crystallize the beginning of a new, hopeful commit=
ment to diversity, equity, and inclusion. Today, as Trump prepares to retur=
n to office, I wonder what would happen if an actress repeated those words =
so publicly.<br/><br/>McDormand=E2=80=99s <i>cri de coeur</i> came to mind =
over the weekend, after Trump nominated
former California G.O.P. vice chair <b>Harmeet Dhillon</b> to head the Just=
ice Department=E2=80=99s civil rights division. Dhillon isn=E2=80=99t exact=
ly Hollywood=E2=80=99s version of a justice warrior. While Silicon Valley w=
as going through its own #MeToo reckoning in 2017, Dhillon=E2=80=94who for =
years has made a habit of filing lawsuits related to hot-button culture war=
 issues=E2=80=94represented <b>James Damore</b>, the Google engineer who wa=
s fired after circulating a 10-page manifesto that critiqued the company=E2=
=80=99s diversity initiatives and suggested that men might be more suited t=
o certain roles in tech. The class-action suit that followed=E2=80=94allegi=
ng discrimination against white male conservatives at Google=E2=80=94was mo=
cked but gained traction in court and ultimately resulted in a settlement, =
paving the way for actress <b>Gina Carano</b>=E2=80=99s Musk-funded suit ag=
ainst Disney. Dhillon became a fixture on Fox News, where she inevitably ca=
ught Trump=E2=80=99s eye. <br/></td>
