d deceptive practices.)<br/><br/>Even without KOSA, the concept of a =E2=80=
=9Cduty of care=E2=80=9D for digital platforms is becoming a major judicial=
 issue. Meta and TikTok face a slew of negligence cases, and A.I. platforms=
